-- UBS taps ex-Citadel exec Kolinsky for market making unit-sources 
-- By John McCrank
-- Wed Mar 26, 2014 10:50AM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, March 26 (Reuters) - UBS AG <UBSN.VX><UBS.N>  is expected to hire former Citadel LLC executive Andy Kolinsky to run sales for its U.S. market-making unit out of Chicago, according to four sources familiar with the matter.

UBS spokeswoman Megan Stinson declined to comment. Kolinsky did not reply to an email asking for comment.